            "value": "<p>Some of Brastlewark's youth craft lesser versions of this snare to prank their friends. A creature that enters the square's square is subjected to a rapid series of flashing lights that overstimulate the senses. They must attempt a @Check[reflex|dc:22] save.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Dazzled] for 2 rounds.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is dazzled for 1 minute.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Blinded] for 1 round and then dazzled for 1 minute.</p>"
